<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="614" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="17.[169,1376,292,597]" pageId="17" pageNumber="614">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[171,523,407,441]" pageId="17" pageNumber="614">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List as a distinct species. Verhagen’s Brush-furred Rat probablywould be best classified as Data Deficient because of lack basic knowledge aboutits life history and ecology.
</paragraph>
